properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const s3 = endctrl.content('Admin').content('ikfkfreekanglessides').transform.position[1];const c2 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C2 Group')('Contents')('C2').size[0] * 0.5;const c1 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C1 Group')('Contents')('C1').size[0] * 0.5;let A, r3a, r3b;try {    A = Math.acos(thisLayer.clamp((c1 - c2) / s3, -1, 1));    r3a = [-(c2 * Math.sin(A)), -(s3 + c2 * Math.cos(A))];    r3b = [-(c1 * Math.sin(A)), -(c1 * Math.cos(A))];} catch (err) {    value;}thisProperty.createPath(points = [[0 - r3a[0], r3a[1]], r3a, r3b, [0 - r3b[0], r3b[1]]], [], [], true);
